title: Uni Hackathon
subtitle: Web3 UniHackathon - April 15 to June 15
description:
As part of AI + Web3 Convention, W3C will host a web3 hackathon for students from April 15th to July 23rd, 2023 with over $100k in grants and prizes.  Students and recent alumni from all universities are welcome to participate. 

 Who can participate: 
 - Ages 18+ only 
 - Team required 
 - University Students
